text: This is... for everyone at 283 Pro...

If there's anything you're concerned about,
just let me know. I'll pass it along to the designer.

...Yes...
But, I really think it's a wonderful outfit...

Haha, I'm glad you think so.
I'll make sure to convey that as well.

Producer-san... um...
I still have so much I don't understand...

In this outfit... I want to be able to stand on that stage...
and shine together with everyone...

S-So... Producer-san,
please continue to support me from now on...

Of course, Mano.
Let's continue to deliver plenty of radiance together.
